name: flowers #7
description:
In your space of colors 
live the most beautiful flowers
one of them brought your verses to my poem

the only thing I could do was to write you 
inhabit your rainbows until I got tired 
and start again

then time passed; life; loves
sleeplessness and travels

finally the distance arrived; to stay

today I release your flower in these lines
today I no longer cry to thank you
